      <title>日元升值引发市场“大规模抛售”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/yen-s-sudden-gain-sparks-widespread-liquidation-across-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元的惊人复苏正在颠覆全球市场，拉动人民币走高，并重创从日本股票到黄金和比特币等资产，因为投资者正在重新评估他们的杠杆押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/yen-s-sudden-gain-sparks-widespread-liquidation-across-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 08:22:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票陷入科技股与其他股票之间的拉锯战：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美联储降息给股市带来的最大好处的板块有所上涨，但全球最大科技公司再度暴跌，导致股市在交易的最后几分钟出现下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 22:35:12 GMT</pubDate>
